        "TileImage": "$($repository 216804b1-e400-4349-b8c9-e7703bd4fdb8).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47.\rToday we have a collaboration with the popular mobile game Brawl Stars. Your targets for elimination: Mosquito sharpshooter Angelo, shy emo boy Edgar and also DJ Frankenstein named Frank.\rOn your side: the beautiful sniper Piper, beautiful cowgirl with a shotgun Shelly, and also the grandfather miner with dynamite named Dynamike.\rIt turns out to be a very interesting game 3 vs 3.\rSo good luck and have fun.\r\rContract by JackMpaint",
